  ${
    $d B w $.  $d F f w x y $.  $d G f w x y $.  $d y z $.
    tfrALT.1 $e |- A = { f | E. x e. On ( f Fn x /\
                A. y e. x ( f ` y ) = ( G ` ( f |` y ) ) ) } $.

    $( Let ` F ` be the union of all acceptable functions. $)
    tfrALT.2 $e |- F = U. A $.
    $( ~ tfr1 via well-founded recursion.  (Contributed by Scott Fenton,
       17-Aug-1994.) $)
    tfr1ALT $p |- F Fn On $=
